{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Add categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata (see [[Wikipedia:Wikidata]]) -->
This template is placed on [[Wikipedia:Category|category pages]] and in [[Wikipedia:Template documentation|template documentation]] to warn about bots, depending on those categories and templates. These pages with this template will be added to [[:Category:Pages monitored by Wikipedia bots]].

== Parameters ==
* Use {{Para|subcats|yes}} to show "This category and subcategories are used by one or more bots." (technically it outputs "This {{var|namespace}} and subcategories are used by one or more bots.") instead of "This {{var|namespace}} are used by one or more bots."
* Use {{Para|bots|<nowiki>*[[User:ExampleBot]] operated by [[User:Example]]</nowiki>}} to list bot usernames (alternatively {{Para|bots|<nowiki>[[Wikipedia:Bots/Requests for approval/Example|Example]]</nowiki>}} can be used)
* Use {{Para|namespace|infobox}} to override the {{para|namespace}} name and show "This infobox is...", etc. Other values can be substituted here.

== Breaking changes ==
<!-- Verbatim copied and adapted from [[Template:Twinkle standard installation]] for use as appropriate here. -->
In the context of this notice, "breaking changes" are any changes to a template that change how it is used, for example adding, removing, or renaming any parameters, or changing the required format of the input to a parameter.

For notice templates (like [[:Category:User warning templates]]), rewordings of the template's contents that change the tone or central message of the template are also considered a breaking change.

== Templatedata ==
<templatedata>
{
    "description": "A message box template to notify about Template or Categories monitored by bots.",
    "params": {
        "namespace": {
            "label": "Namespace",
            "description": "Automatically specifies the namespace of the page (e.g., template, category etc.) use to show others like 'Infobox', .",
            "type": "string",
            "required": false
        },
        "subcats": {
            "label": "Subcategories",
            "description": "Use 'Yes' to Specify whether this template applies to subcategories. (Use only on category namespace)",
            "type": "boolean",
            "required": false
        },
        "bot": {
            "label": "Bot",
            "description": "Other relavent bots username",
            "type": "string",
            "required": false
        },
        "bots": {
            "label": "Bots",
            "description": "Bot username ([[User:ExampleBot]] operated by [[User:Example]]) or list bot usernames alternatively ([[Wikipedia:Bots/Requests for approval/Example|Example]])",
            "type": "string",
            "required": false
        }
    }
}

</templatedata>
